**Summary:** The User Profile API retrieves Amplitude user profiles including user properties, computed user properties, cohort IDs, recommendations, and prediction propensities using GET requests to `https://profile-api.amplitude.com/v1/userprofile` with secret key authentication. This server-side only API requires an Activation plan, supports querying by user_id or device_id, and provides endpoints for fetching recommendations (rec_id), user properties (get_amp_props), cohort memberships (get_cohort_ids), computations (get_computations/comp_id), and prediction propensities (prediction_id/propensity_type).

